Package: atlas-agent
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Sunnyside <engineering@sunnyside.local>
Depends: ca-certificates, ffmpeg, gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0, gstreamer1.0-libav, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, gstreamer1.0-plugins-base, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good, gstreamer1.0-tools, pciutils, python3, python3-gi, systemd, util-linux
Suggests: dkms, docker.io
Description: Atlas onboard vehicle agent and interactive setup
 Atlas Agent connects PX4/MAVSDK telemetry, missions, payload control, and
 accelerator-neutral perception metadata to the Atlas Native ground station.
